data.description: Introducing 820 Meandering Drive, a stunning colonial gem nestled in the heart of Cedar Hill, Texas. This meticulously maintained 2-story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and has recently received a fresh coat of paint inside and out. Step inside to discover a spacious open floor plan that seamlessly connects two inviting living areas and two elegant dining areas, make it the perfect setting for for family gatherings and entertaining. One of the highlights of this property is it's expansive, tree-fenced backyard, providing privacy and serene natural backdrop. Additionally, you'll find a convenient 10x12 shed, offering ample storage space for your outdoor equipment and gardening essentials. Access to this delightful residence is made easy through the alleyway entrance, enhancing the overall appeal of the property. Don't miss the opportunity to make 820 Meandering Drive your new home, where colonial charm meets modern comfort. SELLER Will OFFER 2 POINT BUYDOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER!!
